{"tid":2139974,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【立法會選舉】被DQ不獲發還選舉開支 耗300萬公民黨或陷財政危機","createTime":"2020-08-04T15:45:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-04T15:45:00.000Z","uid":82938,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"997df720dd2cb6705273c13dc3834e36d2be7d47","tid":2139974,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T15:45:00.000Z","msg":"原訂今年9月舉行的立法會選舉在提名期結束當日遭特區政府宣佈延遲，多名民主派參選人則遭選舉主任DQ，政府表明被裁定提名無效者不獲支付選舉開支。有政黨稱，已花費至少300萬元於選舉工程，隨時血本無歸，或觸發財政危機。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200804/QILWWE2HQ4LPM4DVQKWHOZUCSE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200804%2FQILWWE2HQ4LPM4DVQKWHOZUCSE%2F&d=dUSYmziiyXe0H9uVu%2B4Yd0zKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=7e7fa17e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200804%2FQILWWE2HQ4LPM4DVQKWHOZUCSE%2F&h=b5a1ec5b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200804/QILWWE2HQ4LPM4DVQKWHOZUCSE/</a>"}]}